  "remarks": "Voentorg is a contractor of the Ministry of Defence of the Russian Federation. It provides catering and laundry services, as well as military uniforms to the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation. Additionally, Voentorg subsidiary company, Voentorg Retail, sold ‘Russian Army’ T-shirts with the ‘Z’ military symbol, which has been employed by Russian propagandists to promote Russia’s unprovoked and unjustified military aggression against Ukraine.",
